    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Larger and more twisted than the standard wolves, with patches of bioluminescent fungi growing on its hide. It directs the pack with coordinated tactical awareness, bolstering its lesser kin with its presence.</p>",
      "director": "<p><strong>ABILITIES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Coordinating Bite</strong> (Main, Melee, Might): T1 4 dmg; T2 7 dmg + wolf allies in burst 3 gain +1 next attack; T3 10 dmg + wolf allies in burst 3 gain +1 next attack.</li><li><strong>Frenzied Bite</strong> (Main, Melee, Might): T1 4 dmg; T2 8 dmg + 3 ongoing (save ends); T3 12 dmg + 3 ongoing (save ends). On T2-T3 hit, can immediately make another Frenzied Bite on a different target in burst 2.</li><li><strong>Leap and Strike</strong> (Main, Move then Melee): Move up to 20 ft then Bite. On hit, move up to half Speed again.</li></ul><p><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Pack Coordination:</strong> Draugr wolf allies in burst 3 gain +1 to attack rolls.</li><li><strong>Blind Sense:</strong> Cannot be affected by visibility effects. Senses by sound/scent.</li></ul><p>Beat 11, paired with 6 Blind Draugr Wolves. ES 20.</p>",
